hundred times a day, then ninety-nine,

280
00:29:40,879 --> 00:29:41,811
ninety-eight,

281
00:29:43,481 --> 00:29:44,607
ninety-seven,

282
00:29:46,317 --> 00:29:49,377
and then when
I forgot to count,

283
00:29:49,821 --> 00:29:54,724
I was confused on whether
they had black or brown hair,

284
00:29:59,330 --> 00:30:01,321
or if I had
really liked them,

285
00:30:04,068 --> 00:30:06,298
or wonder if
we really did meet

286
00:30:08,473 --> 00:30:10,270
I thought about those things

287
00:30:11,910 --> 00:30:15,311
'96 Soo-in & Kyung-Hee

288
00:30:16,281 --> 00:30:19,773
I'm gonna marry him

289
00:30:20,385 --> 00:30:23,718
He likes you, too?

290
00:30:27,000 --> 00:30:28,088
No

291
00:30:30,895 --> 00:30:32,658
Yes, probably

292
00:30:33,331 --> 00:30:36,357
He always recommends
love stories and poems

293
00:30:36,935 --> 00:30:39,563
And he smiles at me always

294
00:30:43,775 --> 00:30:46,073
Ji-hwan,
can you do me a favor?

295
00:30:59,257 --> 00:31:01,122
He always eats a little

296
00:31:02,126 --> 00:31:03,821
That's why he
doesn't gain weight

297
00:31:04,062 --> 00:31:05,723
It's so irritating

298
00:31:07,065 --> 00:31:09,465
Want me to just
talk to him, right?

299
00:31:09,834 --> 00:31:10,528
Yeah

300
00:31:22,580 --> 00:31:23,604
Hi

301
00:31:23,882 --> 00:31:25,110
Hello

302
00:31:29,454 --> 00:31:30,614
Need a book?

303
00:31:31,356 --> 00:31:32,186
That's okay

304
00:31:32,357 --> 00:31:34,222
I'll pick one out
myself today

305
00:31:36,661 --> 00:31:38,288
He's my friend from church

306
00:31:39,430 --> 00:31:40,158
Hello

307
00:31:40,698 --> 00:31:42,222
Oh, hello

308
00:31:43,735 --> 00:31:45,896
- You pick one out, too
- Okay

309
00:31:48,339 --> 00:31:50,136
Excuse me

310
00:31:52,176 --> 00:31:55,111
What's the most
popular book these days?

311
00:31:56,281 --> 00:31:58,078
What kind of books
do you like?

312
00:31:58,750 --> 00:32:03,483
Well, anything
that's easy to read

313
00:32:04,956 --> 00:32:06,890
Have you ever read
Hu Sam-gwan's Blood?

314
00:32:07,091 --> 00:32:08,626
I already read that...

315
00:32:08,626 --> 00:32:12,221
So...

316
00:32:17,869 --> 00:32:22,863
I heard that this book
is really good

317
00:32:23,408 --> 00:32:24,466
- This one?
- Yes

318
00:32:24,976 --> 00:32:26,773
- It's great
- What is it about?

319
00:32:27,845 --> 00:32:32,305
It's like a detective story.
The author is German

320
00:32:33,818 --> 00:32:35,718
His shoulders are wider
than I thought

321
00:32:36,054 --> 00:32:37,248
I better change the size

322
00:32:38,389 --> 00:32:40,084
Isn't he good-looking?

323
00:32:40,591 --> 00:32:44,357
It seemed as if he
was jealous of you, too

324
00:32:45,096 --> 00:32:48,554
But Ji-yoon,
we look so much alike,

325
00:32:49,067 --> 00:32:51,365
so wouldn't he realize
that we were related?

326
00:32:51,736 --> 00:32:53,533
Look at our nose and mouth

327
00:32:56,107 --> 00:32:59,338
And when a guy knows
some girl likes him,

328
00:32:59,777 --> 00:33:02,473
he'll stay distant,
even if he likes her

329
00:33:03,014 --> 00:33:05,209
No, we don't look
alike at all

330
00:33:05,350 --> 00:33:07,614
Your eyes are more slanted

331
00:33:08,119 --> 00:33:10,383
And you have a
bigger head than me

332
00:33:53,865 --> 00:33:55,389
It's hand-made

333
00:33:57,268 --> 00:33:58,360
I'm not sure

334
00:34:00,204 --> 00:34:02,638
Min-sik!
Come here for a sec

335
00:34:05,676 --> 00:34:07,143
Have you ever
seen this letter?

336
00:34:08,813 --> 00:34:12,305
Oh, this

337
00:34:12,917 --> 00:34:13,884
Do you know it?

338
00:34:15,853 --> 00:34:17,343
Absolutely no idea

339
00:34:18,289 --> 00:34:21,281
There's no address and no name

340
00:34:22,493 --> 00:34:24,222
Who'd sent it like this?

341
00:34:39,444 --> 00:34:40,570
My name is Hang Min-shik

342
00:34:42,080 --> 00:34:43,775
I deliver mail
in a small town

343
00:34:46,350 --> 00:34:49,217
I've been delivering
these strange mails lately

344
00:34:53,624 --> 00:34:55,057
This is her room

345
00:34:58,196 --> 00:35:00,721
I'm in love with this girl

346
00:35:12,944 --> 00:35:14,912
I don't understand

347
00:35:15,346 --> 00:35:18,338
why she doesn't send these letters

348
00:35:23,454 --> 00:35:28,357
But anyhow, I'm just a postman

349
00:35:32,563 --> 00:35:34,793
She's taking
pictures again today

350
00:35:38,269 --> 00:35:44,572
Holding back my wish
to scribble with you together

351
00:35:45,143 --> 00:35:46,906
I told you I'm busy

352
00:35:47,044 --> 00:35:48,636
Just one more question

353
00:35:50,681 --> 00:35:52,740
Are your dreams
often colorful?

354
00:35:53,184 --> 00:35:53,775
- No
- No

355
00:35:55,586 --> 00:35:58,180
It's often for me.
Yes

356
00:35:59,690 --> 00:36:00,714
Here are the results

357
00:36:01,592 --> 00:36:02,752
Kyung-hee and I
are the same type

358
00:36:03,828 --> 00:36:07,025
Someone who has one heart
to love only one person

359
00:36:07,632 --> 00:36:09,395
Never cheats,

360
00:36:09,700 --> 00:36:12,430
but due to obsessiveness,
you're likely to be a stalker

361
00:36:13,371 --> 00:36:17,432
Fantastic.
One heart to love only one person

362
00:36:18,609 --> 00:36:20,372
What about me?
What does it say?

363
00:36:21,479 --> 00:36:25,438
Ji-hwan,
you're the most indecisive

364
00:36:25,816 --> 00:36:28,341
Not any good as a lover

365
00:36:28,886 --> 00:36:32,686
You imagine and decide on your own,
so you're left just liking the girl

366
00:36:33,224 --> 00:36:35,818
If you do date,
you'll break a lot of promises

367
00:36:37,061 --> 00:36:39,052
The worst of their kind

368
00:36:40,031 --> 00:36:41,055
Do you believe that stuff?

369
00:36:41,899 --> 00:36:43,093
That's girls for you

370
00:36:43,834 --> 00:36:45,665
No need to get upset

371
00:36:51,309 --> 00:36:54,642
Soo-in
Go help Ji-hwan

372
00:36:55,546 --> 00:36:57,104
It'll be good exercise

373
00:36:58,683 --> 00:36:59,615
Think so?

374
00:37:07,858 --> 00:37:10,224
Ji-hwan,
what's your blood type?

375
00:37:11,028 --> 00:37:14,054
Not again.
A type

376
00:37:28,613 --> 00:37:31,844
Hey.
What are you doing here alone?

377
00:37:33,251 --> 00:37:35,742
Oh, nothing.
Just hanging out

378
00:37:48,132 --> 00:37:50,657
They're so lucky

379
00:37:52,003 --> 00:37:55,302
Don't they look good together?

380
00:37:57,341 --> 00:38:00,208
It's not easy to fall in love at first sight

381
00:38:02,980 --> 00:38:05,346
It's so wonderful

382
00:38:08,719 --> 00:38:10,186
Gonna stay over, right?

383
00:38:10,821 --> 00:38:12,220
No, I got things to do

384
00:38:12,923 --> 00:38:13,981
Like what?

385
00:38:14,625 --> 00:38:16,252
I told you I gotta go

386
00:38:17,595 --> 00:38:18,391
Kyung-hee

387
00:38:19,964 --> 00:38:23,365
Why do you always ask favors,
and I have to carry them out?

388
00:38:26,003 --> 00:38:29,564
Because you never asked me

389
00:38:31,008 --> 00:38:31,599
Whatever

390
00:38:38,582 --> 00:38:40,675
I'm tired of that face

391
00:38:40,851 --> 00:38:42,409
Always pretending to be weak,

392
00:38:43,120 --> 00:38:45,816
and as if the world will end
if you're not treated well

393
00:38:46,857 --> 00:38:49,451
How long do you think
I'll be by your side?

394
00:38:50,394 --> 00:38:53,591
Tell me.
Tell me!

395
00:38:55,099 --> 00:38:58,000
Kyung-hee, I'm just...

396
00:38:59,136 --> 00:39:00,103
Let's stop

397
00:39:00,871 --> 00:39:02,429
I'm going, bye

398
00:39:50,588 --> 00:39:51,816
Kyung-hee

399
00:39:55,793 --> 00:40:02,130
Just like you,
I don't know what to do

400
00:40:31,028 --> 00:40:33,053
They came at
five in the morning

401
00:40:34,532 --> 00:40:36,056
They ran away

402
00:40:37,001 --> 00:40:39,196
because their parents disapproved

403
00:40:43,741 --> 00:40:45,709
I'm going no matter
what you say

404
00:40:52,349 --> 00:40:53,338
Your turn

405
00:40:57,922 --> 00:41:01,016
I'm going no matter what,
so don't worry. Sorry dad

406
00:41:02,927 --> 00:41:03,586
Good enough?

407
00:41:10,468 --> 00:41:13,995
Here.
Be careful with it

408
00:41:20,778 --> 00:41:22,678
Kyung-hee, it's our school

409
00:41:23,113 --> 00:41:24,580
The gate has changed

410
00:41:25,216 --> 00:41:26,945
Wow, it's been so long

411
00:41:28,686 --> 00:41:30,620
I wish we could go inside

412
00:41:31,222 --> 00:41:32,120
Me, Too

413
00:41:33,491 --> 00:41:35,857
Just ask me,
and I'll do anything

414
00:41:38,128 --> 00:41:39,686
This is so great

415
00:41:49,507 --> 00:41:50,371
Stop!

416
00:41:51,342 --> 00:41:53,367
3767! Stop!

417
00:42:17,568 --> 00:42:19,763
Ji-hwan,
what are you doing?

418
00:42:20,771 --> 00:42:22,671
Just a minute

419
00:42:33,250 --> 00:42:34,217
Come on

420
00:42:36,487 --> 00:42:39,012
Ji-hwan,
someone's down there

421
00:42:39,757 --> 00:42:40,280
What?

422
00:42:44,762 --> 00:42:46,753
Don't wait and
just let it all out

423
00:42:46,997 --> 00:42:48,555
It's fertilizer anyway

424
00:42:49,934 --> 00:42:52,596
I'm sorry
I'm sorry

425
00:42:54,038 --> 00:43:00,068
Oh... my god!

426
00:43:02,179 --> 00:43:05,671
Sure we can see fireflies here?

427
00:43:07,217 --> 00:43:10,880
Yeah. But I think we came too late

428
00:43:11,021 --> 00:43:12,852
Thought they'd still be here

429
00:43:16,660 --> 00:43:17,627
Hey,

430
00:43:18,362 --> 00:43:21,160
let's call the fireflies

431
00:43:22,099 --> 00:43:22,758
How?

432
00:43:23,934 --> 00:43:25,595
I saw it in some book

433
00:43:26,570 --> 00:43:29,300
If you close your eyes
and call them inside,

434
00:43:29,773 --> 00:43:31,934
they'll know to come to you

435
00:43:32,443 --> 00:43:35,003
I don't believe you

436
00:43:36,013 --> 00:43:39,278
Hurry up.
I'm closing my eyes

437
00:44:48,886 --> 00:44:52,413
It's cold!

438
00:45:05,402 --> 00:45:08,565
Hey, how come you guys
are leaving me out?

439
00:45:09,840 --> 00:45:11,671
Isn't she cute?

440
00:45:12,776 --> 00:45:15,939
Yeah.
Sometimes

441
00:45:18,782 --> 00:45:20,409
I want to press her down,

442
00:45:21,985 --> 00:45:25,580
catch her,
and then put her in my pocket

443
00:45:25,989 --> 00:45:27,786
Then take her out
whenever I feel bad

444
00:45:29,827 --> 00:45:30,953
Me, too

445
00:45:33,897 --> 00:45:35,023
Ji-hwan

446
00:45:37,234 --> 00:45:38,861
Thanks for coming with us

447
00:45:40,838 --> 00:45:44,569
If it wasn't for you,
we'd never go on this trip

448
00:45:47,177 --> 00:45:48,804
You see,

449
00:45:49,580 --> 00:45:51,775
we never went on a normal trip before

450
00:45:55,819 --> 00:45:57,184
I'm more grateful

451
00:46:06,964 --> 00:46:07,896
Wait,

452
00:46:08,398 --> 00:46:10,525
where's Kyung-hee?

453
00:46:11,335 --> 00:46:12,165
Kyung-hee?

454
00:46:13,270 --> 00:46:14,066
Huh?

455
00:46:16,306 --> 00:46:19,935
Kyung-hee!

456
00:46:22,346 --> 00:46:24,780
Aren't those her shoes?

457
00:46:35,058 --> 00:46:42,157
Kyung-hee!
Kyung-hee!

458
00:46:45,869 --> 00:46:51,569
Kyung-hee!

459
00:46:52,075 --> 00:46:56,136
I love you my friends!

460
00:46:56,880 --> 00:46:57,642
Hey!

461
00:49:23,660 --> 00:49:24,888
What are you doing here?

462
00:49:25,896 --> 00:49:28,057
You're awake

463
00:49:28,966 --> 00:49:30,957
Is Kyung-hee still sleeping?

464
00:49:31,168 --> 00:49:32,465
Yeah

465
00:49:33,503 --> 00:49:36,907
Didn't you two
sleep in your room?

466
00:49:36,907 --> 00:49:38,709
Because of the mosquitoes,

467
00:49:38,709 --> 00:49:40,677
we couldn't sleep

468
00:49:41,345 --> 00:49:42,612
You must've been really tired

469
00:49:42,612 --> 00:49:45,103
We tried to wake you up
several times

470
00:49:46,016 --> 00:49:47,540
I see

471
00:49:57,127 --> 00:50:01,086
Wanna talk about
our first love for fun?

472
00:50:01,832 --> 00:50:03,129
First love?

473
00:50:03,633 --> 00:50:06,261
It's better than
just sitting here

474
00:50:06,603 --> 00:50:10,266
I like listening to
other people's love stories

475
00:50:11,775 --> 00:50:12,867
Yeah?

476
00:50:13,510 --> 00:50:15,535
Then you go first

477
00:50:16,646 --> 00:50:18,045
um...

478
00:50:19,349 --> 00:50:23,843
In junior high, this girl
worked at a comic book shop,

479
00:50:26,089 --> 00:50:27,758
Because of her big eyes,

480
00:50:27,758 --> 00:50:30,886
everybody seemed
to be attracted to her

481
00:50:31,161 --> 00:50:33,857
She was really popular
among the guys

482
00:50:35,899 --> 00:50:37,667
I went there everyday
to go see her

483
00:50:37,667 --> 00:50:39,931
All the boys liked her
and came to the store

484
00:50:42,305 --> 00:50:43,567
But one day

485
00:50:44,074 --> 00:50:45,769
something happened

486
00:50:48,378 --> 00:50:51,142
Hey, big eyes.
What's your name?

487
00:50:52,749 --> 00:50:55,309
Hey, let me see your face

488
00:50:59,689 --> 00:51:02,055
You pricks,
mind your own business!

489
00:51:05,362 --> 00:51:08,058
Big eyes,
you're my girl

490
00:51:08,598 --> 00:51:10,088
Everybody got that?

491
00:51:18,542 --> 00:51:20,339
I read five of them

492
00:51:24,214 --> 00:51:25,647
You're lying

493
00:51:26,716 --> 00:51:29,186
You only read one

494
00:51:29,186 --> 00:51:31,051
Huh?

495
00:51:32,022 --> 00:51:33,512
What's your name?

496
00:51:34,724 --> 00:51:36,351
Ji-hwan

497
00:51:36,560 --> 00:51:37,549
Lee Ji-hwan

498
00:51:37,994 --> 00:51:40,019
Can you fight well?

499
00:51:40,464 --> 00:51:42,955
Yes, I can

500
00:51:43,233 --> 00:51:45,724
he calls me

501
00:51:45,836 --> 00:51:48,327
but I don't afraid at all

502
00:51:48,705 --> 00:51:50,607
Because she was behind me

503
00:51:50,607 --> 00:51:52,509
I raised my fists,

504
00:51:52,509 --> 00:51:55,034
and went after him
screaming

505
00:51:55,345 --> 00:51:57,280
It was good up till then

506
00:51:57,280 --> 00:51:58,548
And then?

507
00:51:58,548 --> 00:52:00,015
I got beaten

508
00:52:00,250 --> 00:52:02,819
I couldn't hit him even once,

509
00:52:02,819 --> 00:52:04,514
and he almost killed me

510
00:52:04,621 --> 00:52:06,123
So,

511
00:52:06,123 --> 00:52:08,023
she turned her
back on me and left

512
00:52:08,458 --> 00:52:10,392
I guessed she liked macho men

513
00:52:10,594 --> 00:52:12,824
I heard she married him,

514
00:52:13,130 --> 00:52:15,398
and they run a tent bar now

515
00:52:15,398 --> 00:52:16,330
The end

516
00:52:16,566 --> 00:52:17,863
Now, it's your turn

517
00:52:19,703 --> 00:52:21,830
When I was a kid,

518
00:52:22,572 --> 00:52:25,405
I was in the hospital once

519
00:52:26,376 --> 00:52:27,934
That's where

520
00:52:28,879 --> 00:52:30,813
I met him

521
00:52:48,365 --> 00:52:52,199
He was a notorious troublemaker
at that hospital

522
00:52:53,170 --> 00:52:56,469
He played a prank
on the nurses,

523
00:52:56,773 --> 00:52:59,105
and then hid in my room

524
00:53:01,578 --> 00:53:03,478
the first time I saw him,

525
00:53:03,680 --> 00:53:07,480
he smiled really stupid

526
00:53:12,189 --> 00:53:14,282
We became friends quickly,

527
00:53:14,991 --> 00:53:18,188
and my room turned
completely into a playground

528
00:53:20,330 --> 00:53:22,423
He was special

529
00:53:23,533 --> 00:53:25,330
He was very sick,

530
00:53:25,502 --> 00:53:28,869
but a smile never left his face

531
00:53:34,911 --> 00:53:37,971
When I think of it now,
it's really funny,

532
00:53:38,515 --> 00:53:40,984
but I asked people

533
00:53:40,984 --> 00:53:43,214
to call me by his name

534
00:53:43,954 --> 00:53:45,148
Why?

535
00:53:46,723 --> 00:53:50,594
Well, I thought that

536
00:53:50,594 --> 00:53:52,994
even if
we were to split apart,

537
00:53:53,363 --> 00:53:56,264
I'd feel as if
I was always with him

538
00:54:00,804 --> 00:54:02,795
Ji-hwan

539
00:54:04,107 --> 00:54:06,871
What, Soo-in?

540
00:54:24,728 --> 00:54:28,164
We've finally made it

541
00:54:28,164 --> 00:54:30,133
the snow on top of the trees

542
00:54:30,133 --> 00:54:33,068
is so beautiful

543
00:54:34,371 --> 00:54:37,568
people call it snow flowers

544
00:54:37,974 --> 00:54:42,138
Wow, you could be a tour guide

545
00:54:42,779 --> 00:54:44,212
We'll just have
to come this winter

546
00:54:44,514 --> 00:54:46,383
Yeah
Let's come again during winter

547
00:54:46,383 --> 00:54:49,318
I'm serious.
Promise

548
00:54:50,320 --> 00:54:52,922
Promise

549
00:54:52,922 --> 00:54:54,913
Seal

550
00:55:04,567 --> 00:55:07,035
Doesn't seem like
it'll stop raining soon

551
00:55:08,104 --> 00:55:09,773
We'd better hurry

552
00:55:09,773 --> 00:55:13,937
- Yeah, let's hurry
- A little more

553
00:55:14,744 --> 00:55:17,212
Let's stay a little longer

554
00:55:31,027 --> 00:55:34,690
Hold on a little more.
We'll get there soon

555
00:55:39,035 --> 00:55:42,937
Sorry for begging you to come

556
00:55:46,676 --> 00:55:52,615
You know me.
Right?

