I wanna get something
clear to you all

637
01:04:52,154 --> 01:04:55,055
Especially to the ladies here

638
01:04:56,926 --> 01:05:00,129
This woman here
is not my girlfriend

639
01:05:00,129 --> 01:05:02,965
She's just a friend.
Only a friend

640
01:05:02,965 --> 01:05:05,331
Alcohol friend

641
01:05:05,568 --> 01:05:08,304
Please keep your eyes on me

642
01:05:08,304 --> 01:05:10,465
Me, too Me, too

643
01:05:11,674 --> 01:05:18,136
Let's drink!
Asta-la-via!

