677
01:08:39,048 --> 01:08:42,677
Just close them for me

678
01:09:29,565 --> 01:09:33,296
Okay, you can open them now

679
01:09:35,971 --> 01:09:37,404
What was that?

680
01:09:40,376 --> 01:09:45,581
I suddenly remembered a game

681
01:09:45,581 --> 01:09:48,482
I played when I was young

682
01:10:14,610 --> 01:10:15,838
Soo-in,

683
01:10:16,378 --> 01:10:17,970
when you catch a cold,

684
01:10:18,280 --> 01:10:21,613
it's good to
brush your teeth

685
01:10:22,051 --> 01:10:24,849
