717
01:13:47,322 --> 01:13:48,983
Beloved?

718
01:13:50,159 --> 01:13:52,525
I'm not reading it

719
01:13:53,295 --> 01:13:56,822
Okay, I won't do it again

720
01:14:00,102 --> 01:14:01,967
I had a really hard day

721
01:14:03,172 --> 01:14:05,402
I had a hemodialysis twice,

722
01:14:05,841 --> 01:14:09,902
and two
intramuscular injections

723
01:14:10,846 --> 01:14:15,909
But I beared it.
I didn't make a sound

724
01:14:16,785 --> 01:14:18,514
Good

725
01:14:19,288 --> 01:14:22,815
Know what I thought about
to bear it?

726
01:14:25,060 --> 01:14:26,960
You and Ji-hwan

727
01:14:28,464 --> 01:14:30,830
I thought you'd come tell me

728
01:14:31,200 --> 01:14:34,336
