729
01:14:34,336 --> 01:14:36,964
Okay, that's enough

730
01:14:39,074 --> 01:14:41,634
I'll read it on my own

731
01:14:50,219 --> 01:14:54,553
And this is for Ji-hwan

732
01:14:55,791 --> 01:14:59,625
I thought you'd read it
so I was careful

733
01:15:03,832 --> 01:15:09,168
Promise me
you'll give it to him

734
01:15:38,467 --> 01:15:39,835
Hey,

735
01:15:39,835 --> 01:15:43,066
