736
01:15:44,172 --> 01:15:46,936
What were you three
doing all that time?

737
01:15:47,142 --> 01:15:52,444
Don't know where they live
and their numbers?

738
01:16:00,222 --> 01:16:06,161
You're right.
What were we doing?

739
01:16:09,965 --> 01:16:12,900
What have we been doing?

740
01:16:21,843 --> 01:16:24,004
Hello?

741
01:16:25,347 --> 01:16:27,508
Ji-hwan

742
01:16:34,923 --> 01:16:36,720
What's wrong with your hand?

743
01:16:40,329 --> 01:16:42,388
Just an accident

744
01:16:43,665 --> 01:16:48,102
You should be careful

745
01:16:49,705 --> 01:16:50,603
Yeah

746
01:17:00,082 --> 01:17:03,540
I'm really sorry to say this

747
01:17:04,319 --> 01:17:09,120
But we became
uncomfortable around you

748
01:17:13,128 --> 01:17:14,755
You guys now make me

749
01:17:15,897 --> 01:17:18,263
uncomfortable, too

750
01:17:19,701 --> 01:17:21,999
If you're done, then go

751
01:17:22,671 --> 01:17:24,536
It's late

752
01:19:15,951 --> 01:19:20,149
By any chance,
are you Mrs Kim Yeun-soo?

753
01:19:20,288 --> 01:19:21,380
Yes

754
01:19:22,224 --> 01:19:25,523
I'm Lee Ji-hwan,
I called you yesterday

755
01:19:26,661 --> 01:19:29,197
Was it the class of 1996?

756
01:19:29,197 --> 01:19:30,186
Yes

757
01:19:30,632 --> 01:19:34,466
You understand we don't
sell this outside

758
01:19:34,836 --> 01:19:38,966
But you're lucky.
We're almost out of them

759
01:19:39,207 --> 01:19:41,004
Thank you

760
01:19:43,812 --> 01:19:47,339
By the way,
who are you looking for?

761
01:19:47,616 --> 01:19:48,708
Yes?

762
01:19:49,584 --> 01:19:51,677
Well, no

763
01:19:51,987 --> 01:19:56,558
Just that my girlfriend
had lost her yearbook

764
01:19:56,558 --> 01:19:58,293
No, please

765
01:19:58,293 --> 01:20:01,888
I just thought
I could be of some help

766
01:20:02,164 --> 01:20:05,667
