772
01:20:21,650 --> 01:20:24,016
It's two people

773
01:20:24,452 --> 01:20:27,889
One is Kyung-hee.
Kim Kyung-hee

774
01:20:27,889 --> 01:20:31,325
The other is Soo-in?
Shim Soo-in?

775
01:20:32,194 --> 01:20:33,752
Do you know them?

776
01:20:35,130 --> 01:20:38,827
So that's who
you were looking for

777
01:20:39,868 --> 01:20:42,666
Sure, I know them
since they were famous

778
01:20:42,904 --> 01:20:45,634
They were very sick

779
01:20:46,842 --> 01:20:51,074
They barely came to school,
and were always together

780
01:20:51,246 --> 01:20:55,148
Others were both jealous
and sympathetic of them

781
01:20:56,718 --> 01:20:59,812
They were very sick?

782
01:21:00,455 --> 01:21:05,825
My goodness.
You didn't know?

783
01:21:06,661 --> 01:21:12,327
Actually, I was also shocked
when I first heard it

784
01:21:12,734 --> 01:21:17,865
They were absent a lot,
but they never showed it

785
01:21:21,676 --> 01:21:23,610
I'm sorry to tell you this

786
01:21:23,712 --> 01:21:31,084
Soo-in isn't in Seoul anymore,
and Kyung-hee passed away

787
01:21:31,319 --> 01:21:33,116
Pardon?

788
01:21:34,556 --> 01:21:39,425
What are you talking about?
Kyung-hee's dead?

789
01:21:40,896 --> 01:21:43,763
Yes, it's so awful

790
01:21:44,532 --> 01:21:48,332
I was a sophomore then

791
01:21:50,071 --> 01:21:53,199
It's been five years already

792
01:21:54,109 --> 01:21:57,943
Kyung-hee's dead?
Kyung-hee?

793
01:22:02,651 --> 01:22:05,176
Soo-in will be hard to find

794
01:22:05,420 --> 01:22:07,589
After Kyung-hee died,

795
01:22:07,589 --> 01:22:10,786
Soo-in's health got worse

796
01:22:11,359 --> 01:22:12,656
She had it hard

797
01:22:12,761 --> 01:22:16,026
Since they relied on
each other so much

798
01:22:20,902 --> 01:22:24,963
Holding back my wish
to scribble with you together

799
01:22:25,707 --> 01:22:28,335
But Min-sik
will be in late today

800
01:22:28,643 --> 01:22:31,612
Can you tell me
where I find him?

801
01:23:31,806 --> 01:23:34,240
Ji-hwan!

802
01:23:43,852 --> 01:23:52,590
Ji-hwan! Ji-hwan!

803
01:23:55,063 --> 01:23:59,500
Ji-hwan, where did you go?
You scared us

804
01:24:03,304 --> 01:24:05,101
Hi!

805
01:24:29,597 --> 01:24:34,398
* The child I'm looking for

806
01:24:36,337 --> 01:24:42,037
* is hard to see

807
01:24:54,022 --> 01:25:00,518
Do you have a girlfriend now?

808
01:25:14,742 --> 01:25:17,212
Kyung-hee, I found Ji-hwan

809
01:25:17,212 --> 01:25:19,180
I found Ji-hwan

810
01:25:20,215 --> 01:25:24,584
Really? That's great

811
01:25:49,744 --> 01:25:51,644
Hold on

812
01:26:02,357 --> 01:26:06,088
Soo-in, let's change
our names from today

813
01:26:06,227 --> 01:26:08,730
I'm Soo-in and you're Kyung-hee

814
01:26:08,730 --> 01:26:12,300
Why?
Why do you wanna change names?

815
01:26:12,300 --> 01:26:18,637
If we do, even if we're apart

816
01:26:18,873 --> 01:26:24,573
we'll think of each other always

817
01:26:25,079 --> 01:26:29,277
That'll be fun.
You're Soo-in and I'm Kyung-hee

818
01:26:29,784 --> 01:26:33,151
When I think of it now,
it's really funny,

819
01:26:33,421 --> 01:26:38,449
but I asked people
to call me by his name

820
01:26:38,693 --> 01:26:39,887
Why?

821
01:26:41,429 --> 01:26:47,732
Well, I thought that even if
we were to split apart,

822
01:26:47,902 --> 01:26:51,303
I'd feel as if
I was always with him

823
01:27:03,251 --> 01:27:07,153
Next.
Number 42, Shim Soo-in

824
01:27:07,388 --> 01:27:09,379
- Yes
- Yes

825
01:27:14,596 --> 01:27:17,665
Kyung-hee,

826
01:27:17,665 --> 01:27:19,394
Yes

827
01:27:27,208 --> 01:27:30,769
Soo-in -- Kyung-Hee

828
01:27:31,546 --> 01:27:35,744
You're so lucky
to ride on this

829
01:27:37,018 --> 01:27:38,353
You know what?

830
01:27:38,353 --> 01:27:43,658
Nurse Park and Dr Kim
had a fling

831
01:27:43,658 --> 01:27:47,856
They were caught kissing
in the medicine room

832
01:27:48,396 --> 01:27:51,024
- Kyung-hee
- Yeah?

833
01:27:51,966 --> 01:27:54,366
I love you

834
01:27:56,104 --> 01:28:01,371
Me, too

835
01:31:35,456 --> 01:31:37,219
Ji-hwan, she's here

836
01:32:22,403 --> 01:32:24,064
Hi

837
01:32:41,255 --> 01:32:43,223
Hi

838
01:33:02,677 --> 01:33:05,168
Oh yeah, I forgot

839
01:33:05,546 --> 01:33:08,879
You had a small scar here

840
01:33:14,088 --> 01:33:18,787
So this mole
was on the left side

841
01:33:19,260 --> 01:33:21,387
I wasn't sure

842
01:33:54,261 --> 01:34:02,293
Kyung-hee's got a boyfriend

843
01:34:02,436 --> 01:34:07,999
Kyung-hee's got a boyfriend

844
01:34:08,075 --> 01:34:10,009
I'm taking her away!

845
01:34:10,111 --> 01:34:12,841
No!

846
01:34:12,913 --> 01:34:15,177
Don't take her!

847
01:34:24,892 --> 01:34:29,488
It's Ji-yoon, the one who
always borrowed romance novels

848
01:34:29,764 --> 01:34:32,130
Do you remember me?

849
01:34:36,937 --> 01:34:43,740
Hi.
I miss you

850
01:35:26,353 --> 01:35:27,722
Congratulations, be happy

851
01:35:27,722 --> 01:35:28,589
Thanks, go and eat

852
01:35:30,424 --> 01:35:33,518
See you at the reception.
Eat only two servings

853
01:35:35,763 --> 01:35:38,254
Your wish came true.
Congratulations

854
01:35:39,133 --> 01:35:41,192
Congratulations.
Thanks Ji-hwan

855
01:35:41,402 --> 01:35:42,803
Congratulations

856
01:35:42,803 --> 01:35:45,239
Thank you.
Congratulations also

857
01:35:45,239 --> 01:35:47,207
on getting back together

858
01:35:50,945 --> 01:35:54,615
How about a picture for this moment?
I'll take it for you

859
01:35:54,615 --> 01:35:58,953
Should we?

860
01:35:58,953 --> 01:36:00,750
No

861
01:36:02,356 --> 01:36:04,483
You look fine

862
01:36:53,073 --> 01:36:57,407
You have to give it to him

863
01:37:01,949 --> 01:37:10,357
Hi, Ji-hwan. It's Soo-in.
Are you doing okay?

864
01:37:11,258 --> 01:37:18,824
Of course.
Soo-in, are you doing okay, too?

865
01:37:19,300 --> 01:37:23,862
I think I'm going far away

866
01:37:25,439 --> 01:37:29,068
I really don't want to go

867
01:37:29,743 --> 01:37:34,339
What will I do if I
miss you and Kyung-hee?

868
01:37:35,783 --> 01:37:39,617
Ji-hwan,
take care of Kyung-hee

869
01:37:40,855 --> 01:37:44,191
I know without you telling me

870
01:37:44,191 --> 01:37:48,184
that you two like each other

871
01:37:48,729 --> 01:37:53,291
Here's some advice
about Kyung-hee

872
01:37:54,034 --> 01:37:56,400
Kyung-hee's favorite food are

873
01:37:56,704 --> 01:38:01,573
sponge cake with yellow jam
and strawberry juice

874
01:38:01,876 --> 01:38:06,575
And she likes guys
who has a funny bright smile

875
01:38:07,548 --> 01:38:12,144
Look carefully
between her eyes

876
01:38:12,853 --> 01:38:16,957
If she has three wrinkles,
it means she's feeling sick

877
01:38:16,957 --> 01:38:21,985
So send her home quickly

878
01:38:24,632 --> 01:38:29,399
She likes to hold hands,
so do it often

879
01:38:30,704 --> 01:38:33,730
My beloved friend, Ji-hwan

880
01:38:35,175 --> 01:38:44,015
Today I feel like eating the
instant noodles you made for me

881
01:38:48,789 --> 01:38:50,882
Change into this

882
01:38:52,826 --> 01:38:59,133
Dad, you're really handsome,
but there's something missing

883
01:38:59,133 --> 01:39:02,899
What is?

884
01:39:03,470 --> 01:39:06,200
- Dad, come here
- Yes

885
01:39:07,107 --> 01:39:09,769
- Stay still
- Yeah

886
01:39:36,537 --> 01:39:42,567
Hi, Ji-hwan.
It's Kyung-hee

887
01:39:45,045 --> 01:39:47,809
I'm alone right now

888
01:39:48,382 --> 01:39:51,874
My dad suddenly
had to go to Seoul

889
01:39:52,319 --> 01:39:56,949
You better not laugh at this

890
01:39:58,025 --> 01:40:03,429
When I go away,

891
01:40:04,365 --> 01:40:09,462
I told him I wanted a beautiful
funeral like in the movies

892
01:40:10,070 --> 01:40:15,201
It'll probably cost a lot
since I wanted a fitted dress

893
01:40:16,844 --> 01:40:22,583
I wanted to look pretty
for people one last time

894
01:40:22,583 --> 01:40:25,677
Especially you

895
01:40:26,520 --> 01:40:29,580
I'm worried about
your company test

896
01:40:29,857 --> 01:40:34,351
Since you came to see me often,
you didn't have much time

897
01:40:35,162 --> 01:40:41,268
It was awkard and silent
between us,

898
01:40:41,268 --> 01:40:46,296
but I was happy, thinking about the old days.
How about you?

899
01:40:47,641 --> 01:40:51,737
I did, too

900
01:40:52,746 --> 01:40:57,012
I think I'm a very lucky girl

901
01:40:57,418 --> 01:41:02,412
All I have are happy memories

902
01:41:04,158 --> 01:41:09,494
Soo-in, who made me
laugh all the time

903
01:41:12,132 --> 01:41:17,263
And for making me realize how
wonderful taking pictures are,

904
01:41:18,038 --> 01:41:20,871
my beloved Ji-hwan

905
01:41:25,179 --> 01:41:31,084
Ji-hwan, a nice gentleman

906
01:41:31,351 --> 01:41:34,616
who accepted my awkward kiss

907
01:41:36,723 --> 01:41:41,854
This is embarrassing,
but I really liked it then

908
01:41:42,763 --> 01:41:46,790
I want to erase this line

909
01:41:47,000 --> 01:41:49,730
Forget it, I'm too tired

910
01:41:54,808 --> 01:41:57,538
Coming to my funeral, right?

911
01:41:58,212 --> 01:42:03,047
You have to come.
Since I miss you as well

912
01:42:03,317 --> 01:42:05,619
If a single guy
doesn't show up,

913
01:42:05,619 --> 01:42:10,215
people will feel
really sorry for me

914
01:42:11,125 --> 01:42:20,124
Oh yeah, I have something to tell you.
You might get angry at me

915
01:42:21,869 --> 01:42:26,772
Remember that letter
for Soo-in?

916
01:42:27,608 --> 01:42:31,942
I ripped it up

917
01:42:32,312 --> 01:42:37,978
I feel better now
for telling you

918
01:42:39,153 --> 01:42:42,714
You'll forgive me, right?

919
01:42:43,023 --> 01:42:48,689
I'll tell Soo-in
when I meet her

920
01:42:49,630 --> 01:42:55,193
Ji-hwan, I love you

921
01:42:57,237 --> 01:43:04,268
I loved you before
and I love you now

922
01:43:04,545 --> 01:43:10,643
Good-bye, Ji-hwan.
Good-bye
